          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Lorsque cette option est activée, les dépenses prévues programmées après aujourd’hui sont masquées des listes de dépenses."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "When enabled, the app will always launch with the last view you were on instead of defaulting to Home.": {
      "localizations": {
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Cuando está activado, la app siempre abrirá con la última vista usada en lugar de ir al panel."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "When enabled, the app will always launch with the last view you were on instead de defaulting to Accueil."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "When enabled, variable expenses dated after today are excluded from totals and savings calculations.": {
      "localizations": {
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Cuando está activado, los gastos variables posteriores a hoy se excluyen de totales y calculos de ahorro."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Lorsque cette option est activée, les dépenses variables datées après aujourd’hui sont exclues des totaux et des calculs d’épargne."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "When enabled, variable expenses dated after today are hidden from expense lists.": {
      "localizations": {
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Cuando está activado, los gastos variables posteriores a hoy se ocultan de las listas."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Lorsque cette option est activée, les dépenses variables datées après aujourd’hui sont masquées des listes de dépenses."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "When enabled, you’ll always be asked to confirm before anything is deleted.": {
      "localizations": {
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Cuando está activado, siempre se te pedira confirmar antes de eliminar cualquier cosa."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Lorsque cette option est activée, il vous sera toujours demandé de confirmer avant toute suppression."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "When enabled, you’ll be asked to authenticate whenever the app opens.": {
      "localizations": {
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Cuando está activado, se te pedira autenticarte cada vez que se abra la app."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Lorsque cette option est activée, il vous sera demandé de vous authentifier chaque fois que l’app s’ouvre."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "When enabled, your budgets and entries sync across devices with the same Apple ID. When disabled, data stays only on this device.": {
      "localizations": {
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Cuando está activado, tus presupuestos y movimientos se sincronizan entre dispositivos con el mismo Apple ID. Cuando está desactivado, los datos se quedan solo en este dispositivo."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Lorsque cette option est activée, vos budgets et vos entrées se synchronisent sur les appareils utilisant le même identifiant Apple. Lorsqu’elle est désactivée, les données restent uniquement sur cet appareil."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "When I get an email subject contains \"credited to your account\" -> Run Immediately -> Create New Shortcut -> Search for \"Run Shortcut\" -> Add Income From An Email -> Down Arrow -> Input: Choose Variable -> Shortcut Input -> Save.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "new",
            "value": "When I get an email subject contains \"credited to your account\" -> Run Immediately -> Create New Shortcut -> Search for \"Run Shortcut\" -> Add Income From An Email -> Down Arrow -> Input: Choose Variable -> Shortcut Input -> Save."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Cuando reciba un correo cuyo asunto contenga \"credited to your account\" -> Ejecutar inmediatamente -> Crear nuevo atajo -> Buscar \"Ejecutar atajo\" -> Agregar ingreso desde un correo -> Flecha hacia abajo -> Entrada: Elegir variable -> Entrada del atajo -> Guardar."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Quand je recois un e-mail dont l’objet contient \"credited to your account\" -> Executer immediatement -> Creer un nouveau raccourci -> Rechercher \"Executer le raccourci\" -> Ajouter un revenu depuis un e-mail -> Fleche vers le bas -> Entree : Choisir une variable -> Entree du raccourci -> Enregistrer."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "When I get an email subject contains \"Ordered:\" from auto-confirm@amazon.com -> Run Immediately -> Create New Shortcut -> Search for \"Run Shortcut\" -> Add Amazon Expense From Amazon.com -> Down Arrow -> Input: Choose Variable -> Shortcut Input -> Save.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "new",
            "value": "When I get an email subject contains \"Ordered:\" from auto-confirm@amazon.com -> Run Immediately -> Create New Shortcut -> Search for \"Run Shortcut\" -> Add Amazon Expense From Amazon.com -> Down Arrow -> Input: Choose Variable -> Shortcut Input -> Save."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Cuando reciba un correo cuyo asunto contenga \"Ordered:\" de auto-confirm@amazon.com -> Ejecutar inmediatamente -> Crear nuevo atajo -> Buscar \"Ejecutar atajo\" -> Agregar gasto de Amazon desde Amazon.com -> Flecha hacia abajo -> Entrada: Elegir variable -> Entrada del atajo -> Guardar."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Quand je recois un e-mail dont l’objet contient \"Ordered:\" depuis auto-confirm@amazon.com -> Executer immediatement -> Creer un nouveau raccourci -> Rechercher \"Executer le raccourci\" -> Ajouter une depense Amazon depuis Amazon.com -> Fleche vers le bas -> Entree : Choisir une variable -> Entree du raccourci -> Enregistrer."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "When message contains \"credited to your account ending in x1234\" -> Run Immediately -> Create New Shortcut -> Search for \"Run Shortcut\" -> Add Income From An SMS Message -> Down Arrow -> Input: Choose Variable -> Shortcut Input -> Save.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "new",
            "value": "When message contains \"credited to your account ending in x1234\" -> Run Immediately -> Create New Shortcut -> Search for \"Run Shortcut\" -> Add Income From An SMS Message -> Down Arrow -> Input: Choose Variable -> Shortcut Input -> Save."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Cuando un mensaje contenga \"credited to your account ending in x1234\" -> Ejecutar inmediatamente -> Crear nuevo atajo -> Buscar \"Ejecutar atajo\" -> Agregar ingreso desde un SMS -> Flecha hacia abajo -> Entrada: Elegir variable -> Entrada del atajo -> Guardar."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Quand un message contient \"credited to your account ending in x1234\" -> Executer immediatement -> Creer un nouveau raccourci -> Rechercher \"Executer le raccourci\" -> Ajouter un revenu depuis un SMS -> Fleche vers le bas -> Entree : Choisir une variable -> Entree du raccourci -> Enregistrer."
          }
        }
      }
    },
