    "Your screen should look something like this at this point.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Your screen should look something like this at this point."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "En este punto, tu pantalla debería verse más o menos así."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "À ce stade, votre écran devrait ressembler à ceci."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Step 6: Confirm your setup looks right so far.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Step 6: Confirm your setup looks right so far."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Paso 6: Confirma que tu configuración se ve correcta hasta ahora."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Étape 6 : Confirmez que votre configuration semble correcte jusqu’ici."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "To pass transaction amount and merchant details, tap the Amount field, choose Select Variable, then choose Shortcut Input.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "To pass transaction amount and merchant details, tap the Amount field, choose Select Variable, then choose Shortcut Input."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Para pasar el importe de la transacción y los detalles del comercio, toca el campo Importe, elige Seleccionar variable y luego Entrada del atajo."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Pour transmettre le montant de la transaction et les détails du commerçant, touchez le champ Montant, choisissez Sélectionner une variable, puis Entrée du raccourci."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Step 7: Pass Shortcut Input into Amount.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Step 7: Pass Shortcut Input into Amount."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Paso 7: Pasa la Entrada del atajo al campo Importe."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Étape 7 : Passez Entrée du raccourci dans Montant."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Change the Amount field variable to Amount and tap Return. Repeat for Merchant by selecting the Merchant field, choosing Shortcut Input, and changing the variable to Merchant.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Change the Amount field variable to Amount and tap Return. Repeat for Merchant by selecting the Merchant field, choosing Shortcut Input, and changing the variable to Merchant."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Cambia la variable del campo Importe a Importe y toca Retorno. Repite para Comercio seleccionando el campo Comercio, eligiendo Entrada del atajo y cambiando la variable a Comercio."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Changez la variable du champ Montant en Montant et touchez Retour. Répétez pour Commerçant en sélectionnant le champ Commerçant, en choisissant Entrée du raccourci et en changeant la variable en Commerçant."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Step 8: Map Amount and Merchant variables.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Step 8: Map Amount and Merchant variables."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Paso 8: Asigna las variables Importe y Comercio."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Étape 8 : Associez les variables Montant et Commerçant."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The completed shortcut should pass Amount and Merchant correctly. Choose Card and Category in Offshore, set Date to Current Date, tap Return, then tap Save.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "The completed shortcut should pass Amount and Merchant correctly. Choose Card and Category in Offshore, set Date to Current Date, tap Return, then tap Save."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "El atajo terminado debería pasar correctamente Importe y Comercio. Elige Tarjeta y Categoría en Offshore, establece Fecha en Fecha actual, toca Retorno y luego Guardar."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Le raccourci terminé doit transmettre correctement Montant et Commerçant. Choisissez Carte et Catégorie dans Offshore, réglez Date sur Date actuelle, touchez Retour, puis Enregistrer."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Step 9: Finalize fields and save automation.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Step 9: Finalize fields and save automation."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Paso 9: Finaliza los campos y guarda la automatización."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Étape 9 : Finalisez les champs et enregistrez l’automatisation."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Quick Action Pitfalls": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Quick Action Pitfalls"
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Errores comunes de las Acciones rápidas"
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Pièges des actions rapides"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Test each new automation once before creating the next one. Most failures come from wrong variable detail selection in Amount or Merchant.\n\nIf data looks wrong, edit only one field, retest, and continue. Keep changes incremental so troubleshooting stays easy.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Test each new automation once before creating the next one. Most failures come from wrong variable detail selection in Amount or Merchant.\n\nIf data looks wrong, edit only one field, retest, and continue. Keep changes incremental so troubleshooting stays easy."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Prueba cada automatización nueva una vez antes de crear la siguiente. La mayoría de los fallos provienen de elegir mal el detalle de la variable en Importe o Comercio.\n\nSi los datos se ven mal, edita solo un campo, vuelve a probar y continúa. Mantén los cambios incrementales para que la resolución de problemas siga siendo sencilla."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Testez chaque nouvelle automatisation une fois avant de créer la suivante. La plupart des échecs viennent d’une mauvaise sélection du détail de variable dans Montant ou Commerçant.\n\nSi les données semblent incorrectes, modifiez un seul champ, testez de nouveau, puis continuez. Gardez des changements progressifs pour que le dépannage reste simple."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "What Excursion Mode Is": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "What Excursion Mode Is"
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Qué es el Modo excursion"
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ce qu’est le Mode Excursion"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Excursion Mode is a focused tracking mode for high-activity windows when transactions are happening quickly. It prioritizes fast capture so you can stay present while still logging spending accurately.\n\nUse it when real-time awareness matters more than deep entry detail in the moment.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Excursion Mode is a focused tracking mode for high-activity windows when transactions are happening quickly. It prioritizes fast capture so you can stay present while still logging spending accurately.\n\nUse it when real-time awareness matters more than deep entry detail in the moment."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Modo excursion es un modo de seguimiento centrado para ventanas de alta actividad en las que las transacciones ocurren rápidamente. Prioriza la captura rápida para que puedas seguir presente y aun así registrar el gasto con precisión.\n\nÚsalo cuando la atención en tiempo real importe más que el detalle profundo de cada entrada en ese momento."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Le Mode Excursion est un mode de suivi ciblé pour les périodes de forte activité où les transactions se produisent rapidement. Il privilégie une capture rapide pour que vous restiez présent tout en enregistrant les dépenses avec précision.\n\nUtilisez-le lorsque la conscience en temps réel compte davantage que le détail approfondi de chaque entrée sur le moment."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "When To Use It": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "When To Use It"
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Cuándo usarlo"
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Quand l’utiliser"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Use Excursion Mode during travel, outings, event days, or any period with many small transactions. It is especially helpful when waiting until later would cause details to be forgotten.\n\nShort bursts of consistent capture can dramatically improve data quality and reduce end-of-day guesswork.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Use Excursion Mode during travel, outings, event days, or any period with many small transactions. It is especially helpful when waiting until later would cause details to be forgotten.\n\nShort bursts of consistent capture can dramatically improve data quality and reduce end-of-day guesswork."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Usa Modo excursion durante viajes, salidas, días de eventos o cualquier periodo con muchas transacciones pequeñas. Es especialmente útil cuando esperar hasta más tarde haría que se olvidaran detalles.\n\nRáfagas cortas de captura constante pueden mejorar mucho la calidad de los datos y reducir las adivinanzas al final del día."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Utilisez le Mode Excursion pendant les voyages, sorties, journées d’événement ou toute période avec beaucoup de petites transactions. Il est particulièrement utile lorsque remettre la saisie à plus tard ferait oublier des détails.\n\nDe courtes rafales de saisie régulière peuvent améliorer fortement la qualité des données et réduire les approximations en fin de journée."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "How To Work In It": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "How To Work In It"
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Cómo trabajar en él"
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Comment y travailler"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Capture each transaction quickly, then return later for deeper cleanup if needed, such as notes or category refinement. Keep the process simple so you keep momentum.\n\nThe goal in this mode is completeness first, refinement second. A complete draft record is better than a missing one.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Capture each transaction quickly, then return later for deeper cleanup if needed, such as notes or category refinement. Keep the process simple so you keep momentum.\n\nThe goal in this mode is completeness first, refinement second. A complete draft record is better than a missing one."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Captura cada transacción rápidamente y luego vuelve más tarde para una limpieza más profunda si hace falta, como notas o refinamiento de categorías. Mantén el proceso simple para no perder el ritmo.\n\nEl objetivo en este modo es primero la completitud y después el refinamiento. Un borrador completo es mejor que una entrada perdida."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Saisissez chaque transaction rapidement, puis revenez plus tard pour un nettoyage plus poussé si nécessaire, comme les notes ou l’ajustement de catégorie. Gardez le processus simple pour conserver votre élan.\n\nDans ce mode, l’objectif est d’abord l’exhaustivité, puis le raffinement. Un brouillon complet vaut mieux qu’une entrée manquante."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Verify After A Session": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Verify After A Session"
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Verifica después de una sesión"
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Vérifiez après une session"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "When the high-activity window ends, do a short closeout review. Confirm totals align with what you expected and fix obvious mislabels while memory is still fresh.\n\nThis quick wrap-up step keeps excursion sessions accurate and prevents cleanup from piling up later.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "When the high-activity window ends, do a short closeout review. Confirm totals align with what you expected and fix obvious mislabels while memory is still fresh.\n\nThis quick wrap-up step keeps excursion sessions accurate and prevents cleanup from piling up later."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Cuando termine la ventana de alta actividad, haz una breve revisión de cierre. Confirma que los totales coinciden con lo que esperabas y corrige etiquetas claramente incorrectas mientras el recuerdo sigue fresco.\n\nEste paso rápido de cierre mantiene precisas las sesiones de excursion y evita que la limpieza se acumule después."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Quand la période de forte activité se termine, faites une courte revue de clôture. Confirmez que les totaux correspondent à ce que vous attendiez et corrigez les libellés manifestement erronés pendant que la mémoire est encore fraîche.\n\nCette rapide étape de clôture garde les sessions d’excursion précises et évite que le nettoyage s’accumule plus tard."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Excursion Mode Pitfalls": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Excursion Mode Pitfalls"
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Errores comunes del Modo excursion"
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Pièges du Mode Excursion"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Avoid over-editing entries in the moment, because that usually leads to skipped capture. Focus on fast capture first.\n\nAlso avoid skipping the post-session review. Fast entry is great for speed, but the short cleanup pass is what locks in long-term accuracy.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Avoid over-editing entries in the moment, because that usually leads to skipped capture. Focus on fast capture first.\n\nAlso avoid skipping the post-session review. Fast entry is great for speed, but the short cleanup pass is what locks in long-term accuracy."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Evita editar demasiado las entradas en el momento, porque eso suele llevar a omitir capturas. Concéntrate primero en capturar rápido.\n\nTambién evita saltarte la revisión posterior a la sesión. La entrada rápida es excelente para la velocidad, pero el breve repaso de limpieza es lo que asegura la precisión a largo plazo."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Évitez de trop modifier les entrées sur le moment, car cela conduit souvent à manquer des saisies. Concentrez-vous d’abord sur une capture rapide.\n\nÉvitez aussi de sauter la revue après la session. La saisie rapide est excellente pour la vitesse, mais c’est le court passage de nettoyage qui garantit la précision à long terme."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Overview": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Overview"
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Resumen general"
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Aperçu"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Home Overview": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Home Overview"
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Resumen de Panel"
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Aperçu d’Accueil"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Home is the fastest way to understand where the current period stands before opening detailed screens. It brings spending, income, and savings signals into one place so you can decide what needs attention first. Start here at the beginning of each check-in, then drill into Budgets, Income, or Accounts for corrections.\n\nUse the widgets as directional signals, not isolated verdicts. When a tile looks unusual, validate the cause in the destination screen that owns that data. This keeps day-to-day decisions tied to real entries instead of quick assumptions.\n\nA good Home workflow is simple: scan, identify one priority, investigate, then return. Repeating that loop keeps your budgeting process focused and consistent. Over time, Home becomes your control panel for staying proactive rather than reactive.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Home is the fastest way to understand where the current period stands before opening detailed screens. It brings spending, income, and savings signals into one place so you can decide what needs attention first. Start here at the beginning of each check-in, then drill into Budgets, Income, or Accounts for corrections.\n\nUse the widgets as directional signals, not isolated verdicts. When a tile looks unusual, validate the cause in the destination screen that owns that data. This keeps day-to-day decisions tied to real entries instead of quick assumptions.\n\nA good Home workflow is simple: scan, identify one priority, investigate, then return. Repeating that loop keeps your budgeting process focused and consistent. Over time, Home becomes your control panel for staying proactive rather than reactive."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Panel es la forma más rápida de entender en qué punto está el periodo actual antes de abrir pantallas detalladas. Reúne señales de gasto, ingresos y ahorro en un solo lugar para que puedas decidir primero qué necesita atención. Empieza aquí al inicio de cada revisión y luego profundiza en Presupuestos, Ingresos o Cuentas para hacer correcciones.\n\nUsa los widgets como señales de dirección, no como veredictos aislados. Cuando una tarjeta se vea inusual, valida la causa en la pantalla de destino que posee esos datos. Así mantienes las decisiones del día a día ligadas a entradas reales en lugar de suposiciones rápidas.\n\nUn buen flujo de trabajo en Panel es simple: escanea, identifica una prioridad, investiga y vuelve. Repetir ese ciclo mantiene tu proceso de presupuesto enfocado y consistente. Con el tiempo, Panel se convierte en tu centro de control para actuar de forma proactiva y no reactiva."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Accueil est le moyen le plus rapide de comprendre où en est la période en cours avant d’ouvrir des écrans détaillés. Il rassemble les signaux de dépense, de revenu et d’épargne au même endroit pour que vous puissiez décider d’abord ce qui demande de l’attention. Commencez ici au début de chaque point de contrôle, puis approfondissez dans Budgets, Revenu ou Comptes pour corriger.\n\nUtilisez les widgets comme des signaux de direction, pas comme des verdicts isolés. Lorsqu’une tuile paraît inhabituelle, validez la cause dans l’écran de destination qui possède ces données. Cela garde les décisions du quotidien liées à de vraies entrées plutôt qu’à des suppositions rapides.\n\nUn bon flux de travail dans Accueil est simple : scanner, identifier une priorité, enquêter, puis revenir. Répéter cette boucle garde votre processus budgétaire concentré et cohérent. Avec le temps, Accueil devient votre panneau de contrôle pour rester proactif plutôt que réactif."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The Home dashboard acts as a starting point for daily review. Read top-level totals first, then look for any widget that suggests a shift in spending, income, or savings direction. When something needs clarification, open the matching core screen and validate the underlying entries. Returning to Home after each adjustment helps you confirm whether the correction improved the period outlook.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "The Home dashboard acts as a starting point for daily review. Read top-level totals first, then look for any widget that suggests a shift in spending, income, or savings direction. When something needs clarification, open the matching core screen and validate the underlying entries. Returning to Home after each adjustment helps you confirm whether the correction improved the period outlook."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "El panel de Panel actúa como punto de partida para la revisión diaria. Lee primero los totales principales y luego busca cualquier widget que sugiera un cambio en la dirección del gasto, los ingresos o el ahorro. Cuando algo necesite aclaración, abre la pantalla principal correspondiente y valida las entradas subyacentes. Volver a Panel después de cada ajuste te ayuda a confirmar si la corrección mejoró la perspectiva del periodo."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Le tableau de bord d’Accueil sert de point de départ à la revue quotidienne. Lisez d’abord les totaux principaux, puis cherchez tout widget qui suggère un changement dans la direction des dépenses, du revenu ou de l’épargne. Quand quelque chose demande une clarification, ouvrez l’écran principal correspondant et validez les entrées sous-jacentes. Revenir à Accueil après chaque ajustement vous aide à confirmer si la correction a amélioré la perspective de la période."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Use Home as your first scan, then open the matching screen to verify any number that looks off.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Use Home as your first scan, then open the matching screen to verify any number that looks off."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Usa Panel como primer vistazo y luego abre la pantalla correspondiente para verificar cualquier cifra que se vea mal."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Utilisez Accueil comme premier balayage, puis ouvrez l’écran correspondant pour vérifier tout chiffre qui semble incorrect."
          }
        }
      }
    },
